'''Telifuon''', ar jos '''fuon''', a wah [[telikomiunikieshan]] divais we lou tuu ar muo yuuza fi kandok kanvasieshan wen deh de tuu for apaat fi ie deh wananeda direkli. Di telifuon kanvoert [[song]], tipikali ah muos ifishentli di [[yuuman vais]], ina hilekchanik signal suutebl fi [[chanzmishan]] vaya kiebl ar adaels chanzmishan miidia uoba lang distant, ah riiplie demde signal siehwan siehtaim ina aadibl faam tu iyuuza.
